The paper deals with the elicitation and debugging of formal specifications for Cyber-Physical Systems, which involves software engineering (cs.SE) and systems engineering (cs.SY). The paper also presents two debugging algorithms, which involve programming languages and compilers (cs.PL) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the analysis of reactive requirements, which involves logic (cs.LO).
